data.description: Beautiful, updated home sitting on almost an acre in Carlyss. This 3-bedroom, 2 bath home is move in ready and offers many amenities. Outside, there is a storage building, two RV hookups, a covered front porch, covered parking for two cars, and a large back deck. The inside of the home offers an open floor plan with lots of room for entertaining. Amenities include a wood burning fireplace, tile flooring, wood flooring, tile backsplash, carrara marble countertops, and a gorgeous primary suite with a soaking tub. This is a must see. Flood Zone X which means flood insurance is typically not required.
